Copy provided ebuild files into local portage overlay (e.g. /usr/local/portage)

cp -R gentoo/net-analyzer/ /usr/local/portage

Set wanted keyword for release version:
echo "net-analyzer/flowgrind ~amd64" > /etc/portage/package.keywords/flowgrind 
(OR)
Set wanted keyword for git version:
echo "net-analyzer/flowgrind ** > /etc/portage/package.keywords/flowgrind 

(optional) enable use flags for optional feature sets:
euse --enable gsl; euse --enable pcap

Install flowgrind:
emerge flowgrind
